Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:03.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,小島  你要是一塊巧克力都沒收到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:04.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就分你一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:06.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不  我已經收到兩塊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:07.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}早上好  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:08.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天是情人節呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:11.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我開始緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:12.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:12.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,2月14日  在這人人為之興奮的節日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:18.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學今年肯定也會乘此機會來捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:20.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:23.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不能被她迷惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:26.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:29.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還準備了三份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:32.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  你還太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:35.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,反正就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:38.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,或是像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:41.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,又或是像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:44.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我早就看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:46.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,來吧  放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:53.44,Takagi san—Picture 11-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz312.4\pos(1138,624)\fs90\t(0,6000,\fs110)}致學長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,包裝得還真精緻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:52.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,致學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:55.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:01:00.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完全搞不懂高木同學想怎麼捉弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:03.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哪一封看上去都不像是高木同學寫的字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:12.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,給學長  我在文化祭的時候喜歡上你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:11.88,Takagi san—Picture 11-1,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\pos(902,420)}致學長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:11.88,Takagi san—Picture 11-1,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\an1\pos(492,738)}我在文化祭的\N時候喜歡上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:11.88,Takagi san—Picture 11-1,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\pos(742,902)}請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:19.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,難道說  這不是高木同學送的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而是學妹送的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:23.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且還有三份
