Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:10.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上好  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:14.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上好  高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天也來得非常早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:20.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,久違地騎自行車來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是這樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:28.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可不能讓高木同學問起巧克力的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:29.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我說西片…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天是幾號來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:34.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不能慌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:38.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學會像這樣拿情人節來捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:42.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明昨天就已經預料到了  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:46.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我已經想好了該怎麼回敬她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:50.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  今天是2月14日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:51.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是小魚乾日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎  高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.92,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1094,994)}                   ni    ichi   yon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在黑板上寫上「2」「1」「4」看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:03:58.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.72,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1068,996)}               bo-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,把「1」讀作棒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.45,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1026,994)}         niboshi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就會念成小魚乾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60}註：數字4在日語中既能讀作yon也能讀作shi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,數字的諧音梗呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有些牽強就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  這是正式的紀念日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:17.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,話說西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你剛剛是不是想藏什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:24.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同學  真敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:28.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不繼續岔開話題的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:35.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為了慶祝小魚乾日  我們用諧音梗來對話怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:38.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,用諧音梗來對話？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒錯  那麼先從我開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,猜錯了就算輸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:51.20,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,994)}ohayou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:51.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:51.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs90\fad(500,450)}註：這裡0當作o，8念作ha，4念作yon即與「早上好」相似
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:51.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  我說對了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這個可能太簡單了點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了  下面輪到高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看我一下給你猜出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:08.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,情…人…節？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原來不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:16.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我寫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.13,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1186,992)}                      barebare
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太簡單了  答案是完全暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:28.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,意思是  我偷藏巧克力的事情完全暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:30.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.14,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1070,994)}      harebare
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,答案是  晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:36.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我是想告訴你今天是個晴朗的好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:42.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,用諧音梗來表達真難呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:43.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雖說有些模稜兩可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是可以算西片猜錯輸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:50.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還好沒猜對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼懲罰遊戲  要讓你做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:06:02.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,話說  為什麼我要拚命向高木同學隱瞞巧克力的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:08.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明只要跟她說  其實有學妹送我巧克力就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:13.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對了  讓我看看作業就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:17.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,作業？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:18.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有一個問題想向你請教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這就是輸了比賽的懲罰遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學竟然會向我請教作業
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,現在把包打開的話  巧克力會被看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:36.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,事到如今  還是向高木同學坦白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:45.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她可能還會和我討論一下我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:50.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可能我是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:57.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,坦白的時機…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,話說回來  要是平時的高木同學的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,會更變本加厲地捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,會找到巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然後哈哈大笑才對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,情人節快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:23.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,情人節快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你這是打的什麼招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:30.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我覺得情人節跟聖誕節差不多快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:34.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以  聖誕老人美奈要送你們禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:37.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今年只為你倆用心準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:38.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:48.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我們三人間的友情有著比巧克力更堅硬的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:51.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這份禮物裡蘊含著我的這份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,美奈  你竟然把我們看得這麼重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:57.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  友情的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,已經融化得不成樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:02.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:05.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我明明記得我放進冰箱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是不是因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:13.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上還以為不見了  原來在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,暖寶寶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我明明那麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不用哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友情融為一體  三人一體的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:27.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看起來也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:31.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啦  我也有東西要送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雖然不是親手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:46.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然是三個臭皮匠頂個諸葛亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,情人節快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,中井  這個送你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:08.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哦  難道說是巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,噓  你聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,會被田邊老師聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,情人節…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:17.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,濱口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你想要巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果你願意給我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是麼  給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,快點收下啊  老師會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:43.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:45.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:50.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:54.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這個…不是親手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:59.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,昨天我剛好在超市看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,北條在買做巧克力的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果她沒有送我親手做的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:10.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,意思就是那才是本命巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:14.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,給了我以外的某個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:17.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有得拿就不錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我替你吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,安慰我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:23.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比較級的詞尾加「er」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,最高級的詞尾加「est」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  有幾個例外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:36.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}比如「beatiful」之類比較長的形容詞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比較級加上「more」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,成為「more beatiful」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}最高級加上「most」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那個西片  講到其他頁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}變成「most beatiful」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:54.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:55.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果是平時的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:11:00.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,應該會設下一堆情人節專屬的圈套才對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:04.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣就找不到和她說巧克力那事的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那就由我出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我說高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:13.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要不要和我比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:14.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比橡皮擦屑的長度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:22.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,像這樣擦到它斷掉為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,擦得長的人算贏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這招我還沒練到家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原本計劃等到擦出2.5厘米的屑以後再向她挑戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:44.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但這裡要拋下自尊故意輸給她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:45.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:49.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,耶  我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:51.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:52.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,作為懲罰遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只好不情願地把我的秘密告訴高木同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣就很自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那可以從我開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:03.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣下去感覺要輸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,畢竟是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,肯定會捉弄我來搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:18.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:23.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,3.5厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大幅刷新自己的紀錄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:34.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼非要在想輸的時候超常發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:35.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:36.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,恭喜你西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:39.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼回事  高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼不來捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,接下來到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:43.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:44.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:45.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的請你加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學的話應該能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:51.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不錯哦  就是這樣高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我說啊西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果我贏了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,當…當然  我什麼都會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:57.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:01.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那作為懲罰  我坦白一個秘密怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然今天還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學竟然會放棄比賽  真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是不是要下大雪了…不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:12.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼雪啊  簡直是要下隕石了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:16.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,別這樣  加把勁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,需要加把勁的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:23.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「beautiful」的比較級和最高級是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,beautifuler  beautifulest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:29.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  你果然沒聽課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是的  這裡會考的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,別忘了複習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了  是平時的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,櫻井同學很高興地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,快回來  別讓他們得分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  放學去趟零食店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:56.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啊  自掏腰包狂吃巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,必須跟高木同學說才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:02.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片學長在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:09.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  有人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:18.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:22.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那個…學長  我們的巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:23.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:25.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你這個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是說這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:32.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:39.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  連你也加入那邊的陣營了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:40.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真好啊  竟然有三份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然後我給了爸爸後…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:46.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是對不起  我不能收下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:53.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雖然我特別高興  但…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:58.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:14:59.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:03.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,其實我們搞錯了鞋櫃的位置  放錯地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是的  都怪你說學長的鞋櫃就在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  看錯了一行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:13.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以麻煩你叫下柴崎學長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,柴崎學長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在文化祭演的小狗真的很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:29.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那個  請收下我們的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:29.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你早點吃掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:34.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:35.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:39.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這下就不必向高木同學保留多餘的秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,說起來高木同學去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,天空好澄澈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嘴巴乾嘛張這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:02.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,北條
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跟僵屍一樣怪嚇人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:06.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,建議你別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以  你在消沉什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我才沒有消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,少騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:16.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你只要做這個動作就是在消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:19.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你覺得我們有多少年的交情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為收到的巧克力少得可憐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,北條怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:36.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,本命巧克力  有好好送出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:37.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,本命？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不用瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:41.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你有親手做巧克力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:47.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我在超市偶然看到你在買材料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,全…全都融化掉失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就少盯了一會兒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會融化得那麼快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我的失敗就那麼好笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:09.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,算了  你恢復精神了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:14.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  給我的巧克力是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:23.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,白色情人節請給我高級的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:33.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對啊  今年沒有收到高木同學的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,話說我才沒有在期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:42.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:03.72,Takagi san—Picture 11-3,,0,0,0,,{\frz355.3\pos(556,892)}明天能早點來學校嗎？我有東西想給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.02,Takagi san—Picture 11-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(582,896)\frz354.7}明天早點來學校的話可能會有好事發生哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.27,Takagi san—Picture 11-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,884)\frz354.7}有什麼想要的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.91,Takagi san—Picture 11-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(812,230)\frz355.8}現在能見上一面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:30.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:46.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:49.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為看到你自行車停在那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:50.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那…那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,其實今天我收到來自學妹的巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,最後好像是搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:07.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是給我而是要給柴崎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:11.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但我是想跟高木同學說我收到巧克力這件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:13.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,卻遲遲開不了口  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:14.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,欸  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:16.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:17.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:20.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,害得我一直心裡不踏實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:21.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也一直在忐忑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:31.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不太想聽西片跟我說收到巧克力的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:37.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,感覺一旦聽了  又會變成之前那個壞心眼的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不想變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:44.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然後就不能順利捉弄西片了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有點討厭那樣的自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:53.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  該道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,讓你心情變糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:08.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,奇怪  高木同學怎麼知道我收到巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:11.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,給  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:19.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,其實我早上就想放到西片的鞋櫃裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雖然覺得明天再給也行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但還是想在2月14號這天送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你能收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:34.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:38.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可以打開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:43.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:45.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,小魚乾？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:49.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,2月14號是小魚乾日對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:58.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片說小魚乾日的時候  我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:01.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我們的想法漸漸相近了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為在一起的時間太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這個是給貓咪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:10.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:11.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片的是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:14.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:18.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了  能在2月14號這天送到你手上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:21.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,心情總算是轉晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:25.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  橡皮擦的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明天再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:28.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不過贏的肯定是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:32.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那種事誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:34.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:44.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  濱口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:47.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,重要的事是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼  你打算去表白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,白色情人節時我要跟北條表白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:57.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,表…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:00.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以西片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到那天你就去跟高木同學表白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:05.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:12.02,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}スノーマジックファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:15.82,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の魔法にかけられて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:19.49,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}僕は君に恋した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:24.52,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もしかして君は雪の妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.69,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君が住む山は「スノーランド」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:36.33,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}一年中雪の降るこの国で    私は生まれたのと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:39.56,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君は話してくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:46.48,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ねぇ    私は夏を見たことがないの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:56.44,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}燃えるようなあの夏を    それを見るのが私の夢なの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:22:58.93,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}でも良いの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:07.00,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}この世界は知らない方がロマンチックな事も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:13.24,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}たくさんあるのでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:17.24,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}スノーマジックファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:21.07,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の魔法にかけられて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:24.73,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}僕は君に恋した
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:28.85,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もしかして君は雪の精？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:37.25,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の妖精とのファンタジー
