Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:15.82,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}被施加了雪之魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:19.49,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我對你一見傾心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:24.52,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}難道你就是雪之妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.69,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你住在名為「雪國」的大山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:36.33,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}降生於終年飄雪的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:39.56,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你曾對我如是訴說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:46.48,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}吶  我從未見過盛夏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:56.44,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}看那熾熱如火的盛夏  是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:22:58.93,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不過無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:07.00,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}在這個世界上還有許多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:13.24,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因為未知才有的浪漫對吧
